high_descs: Walk to the kitchen and then stand in front of the diningtable.
Pick up a potato from the table.
Take the potato to the bathroom and stop in front of the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, wash it then remove it.
Look around the sink for a while.
Leave the bathroom with the potato from the sink.
anns.task_desc: Getting the potato and washing it in the sink.

high_descs: Leave the room take a right and go into the door on your right.
Pick up the potato on the plate on the table.
Leave the room and go to the wall that is straight ahead and take a left into the bathroom and take the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, rinse it off and take it out.
Step a little to your left towards the sink.
Put the potato on the upper left ledge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a potato and leave it on the sink.

high_descs: Turn around go near the dining table.
Take the potato from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the potato into the sink and washed it.
Take it out and go near the sink.
Put the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the sink.
